Interface PwRewardedVideoAd.PwRewardedVideoAdListener

  • Enclosing class:
    PwRewardedVideoAd

    public static interface PwRewardedVideoAd.PwRewardedVideoAdListener
    Implement this interface to be notified of rewarded video ad lifecycle changes.

    • Method Detail

      • rewardedVideoDidLoad

        void rewardedVideoDidLoad(PwRewardedVideoAd rewardedVideoAd,
                          TVASTRewardedVideoInfo rewardedVideoInfo)
        This event is fired once rewarded video content is fully downloaded and is ready to be displayed.
        Parameters:
        rewardedVideoAd - the rewarded video ad that caused the event.
        rewardedVideoInfo - contains remaining views, start views, successful viewings since the tracking horizon.

      • rewardedVideoDidClose

        void rewardedVideoDidClose(PwRewardedVideoAd rewardedVideoAd,
                           TVASTRewardedVideoInfo rewardedVideoInfo)
        This event is fired once the rewarded video ad closes, and your application is back in focus.
        Parameters:
        rewardedVideoAd - the rewarded video ad that caused the event
        rewardedVideoInfo - contains remaining views, start views, successful viewings since the tracking horizon.

      • rewardedVideoDidFail

        void rewardedVideoDidFail(PwRewardedVideoAd rewardedVideoAd,
                          String error,
                          TVASTRewardedVideoInfo rewardedVideoInfo)
        This event is fired if the rewarded video ad request fails to return an ad.
        Parameters:
        rewardedVideoAd - the rewarded video ad that caused the event
        error - description of the error that occurred. The error messages are intended to provide information for developers and should not be displayed to the user.
        rewardedVideoInfo - contains remaining views, start views, successful viewings since the tracking horizon. Also contains error code returned from server.

      • rewardedVideoActionWillLeaveApplication

        void rewardedVideoActionWillLeaveApplication(PwRewardedVideoAd rewardedVideoAd,
                                             TVASTRewardedVideoInfo rewardedVideoInfo)
        This event is fired just before the app will be sent to the background.
        Parameters:
        rewardedVideoAd - the rewarded video ad that caused the event
        rewardedVideoInfo - contains remaining views, start views, successful viewings since the tracking horizon.

      • rewardedVideoDidEndPlaybackSuccessfully

        void rewardedVideoDidEndPlaybackSuccessfully(PwRewardedVideoAd rewardedVideoAd,
                                             RVSuccessInfo rewardedVideoSuccessInfo,
                                             TVASTRewardedVideoInfo rewardedVideoInfo)
        This event is fired when protocol for reward the user is approved.
        Parameters:
        rewardedVideoAd - rewarded video ad that caused the event.
        rewardedVideoSuccessInfo - all the info about the success event of the rewarded video data like currency, amount, remaining views.
        rewardedVideoInfo - remaining views, start views, successful viewings data before the add started play.
